open-youtube-transcript-copy is an unofficial open fork generated from the
Mozilla Add-ons package for "YouTube Transcript Copy".

Mozilla Add-ons reports the upstream add-on license as MIT License. Upstream
package metadata, author attribution, version, download URL, and SHA-256 hash
are recorded in UPSTREAM.md and .mirror/amo.json when the updater runs.

This repository is not affiliated with or endorsed by the original author.
